cdata.name: Aukcecoin
cdata.desc:
Aukce is a tokenized gamer platform. It provides users with bank-like services forthe gamers community, such as bidding, storage, and payment tools, also it is possible to bet on games and earn rewards in tokens. Aukce users will be able to accessits availableeconomic features from their smartphone since the platform has a mobile support.

The AUK token is the platform native cryptocurrency. It will act as the mean to perform in-game transactions and it will be possible to trade it on external Exchanges.
